<strong>1. Installing</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">$ npm i gblapi.js
</code></pre>
<p><strong>2. Creating a Glenn Client</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-js"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> GBL = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">"gblapi.js"</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">//Require the module, you can use import like so:</span>
